1
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:42,060
=Twin Fire Dawn=

2
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:45,060
=Episode 17=

3
00:00:55,940 --> 00:00:56,900
Go.

4
00:00:58,900 --> 00:00:59,860
Commander.

5
00:01:03,700 --> 00:01:05,020
Madam is here too.

6
00:01:05,340 --> 00:01:06,460
Xue Wan?

7
00:01:10,580 --> 00:01:11,880
So you're Xue Wan.

8
00:01:12,720 --> 00:01:14,620
Looks like the Commander
already knows everything.

9
00:01:14,700 --> 00:01:16,540
That saves me a lot of trouble.

10
00:01:17,100 --> 00:01:17,940
Xinran.

11
00:01:18,300 --> 00:01:19,420
We have guests here.

12
00:01:19,540 --> 00:01:20,870
Why wasn't I informed?

13
00:01:21,340 --> 00:01:21,940
I...

14
00:01:24,440 --> 00:01:25,699
I'm sorry, Commander.

15
00:01:25,700 --> 00:01:26,900
Gu Nianchi.

16
00:01:27,380 --> 00:01:29,379
Didn't you already know I was Xue Wan?

17
00:01:29,380 --> 00:01:29,899
She...

18
00:01:29,900 --> 00:01:30,859
Zhuang Yunqiu.

19
00:01:30,860 --> 00:01:32,179
She's just my dowry maid.

20
00:01:32,180 --> 00:01:34,140
I'm the true daughter of the Xue family.

21
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:36,020
I think you've misunderstood, Miss Xue.

22
00:01:36,980 --> 00:01:38,760
The person I want
to marry is Zhuang Yunqiu.

23
00:01:39,180 --> 00:01:40,940
Whether she's a maid or a young lady,

24
00:01:43,460 --> 00:01:46,180
she's the only woman
who'll stay by my side.

25
00:01:47,940 --> 00:01:48,820
Shaoyuan.

26
00:01:50,260 --> 00:01:51,630
What are you saying?

27
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:54,460
I believe I've made myself very clear.
Miss Xue.

28
00:01:55,880 --> 00:01:57,560
My wife and I still
have matters to discuss.

29
00:01:57,560 --> 00:01:58,640
We won't keep you any longer.

30
00:01:58,820 --> 00:01:59,660
Xinran.

31
00:02:00,060 --> 00:02:00,940
See Miss Xue out.

32
00:02:02,700 --> 00:02:03,460
Xue Wan.

33
00:02:03,500 --> 00:02:04,539
I'll explain everything

34
00:02:04,540 --> 00:02:06,540
to you properly someday.

35
00:02:06,870 --> 00:02:07,589
Zhuang Yunqiu.

36
00:02:07,590 --> 00:02:08,460
You...

37
00:02:13,980 --> 00:02:15,179
You want me to leave?

38
00:02:15,180 --> 00:02:16,460
Well, I'm not leaving.

39
00:02:21,540 --> 00:02:22,660
Miss.

40
00:02:22,780 --> 00:02:24,640
Why don't I take you home first?

41
00:02:25,500 --> 00:02:26,460
Xinran.

42
00:02:26,540 --> 00:02:28,700
Even you're siding
with that Zhuang Yunqiu now?

43
00:02:28,820 --> 00:02:30,460
Of course not, Miss.

44
00:02:30,700 --> 00:02:32,859
You must've been tricked
by Zhuang Yunqiu.

45
00:02:32,860 --> 00:02:34,660
That's why you
let her marry in your place.

46
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:37,600
She's been throwing her weight around
inside the Commander's Residence.

47
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:40,140
Even the Commander listens to her.

48
00:02:40,220 --> 00:02:42,379
Just because I know who she really is,

49
00:02:42,380 --> 00:02:43,839
she keeps threatening me,

50
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,699
saying she'll slash my face

51
00:02:45,700 --> 00:02:47,540
and make the Commander
wipe out my whole family.

52
00:02:48,540 --> 00:02:50,060
Zhuang Yunqiu.

53
00:02:50,180 --> 00:02:52,020
I really misjudged you.

54
00:02:54,300 --> 00:02:55,180
Xinran.

55
00:02:55,200 --> 00:02:57,960
Come back with me. We don't need to
stay here and suffer this humiliation.

56
00:02:58,700 --> 00:03:00,300
Thank you for your kindness, Miss.

57
00:03:00,420 --> 00:03:02,369
Young Master has never liked me.

58
00:03:02,370 --> 00:03:04,340
I'd better not go back
and make myself unwelcome.

59
00:03:04,980 --> 00:03:07,179
I'll stay here and help you
keep an eye on Zhuang Yunqiu.

60
00:03:07,180 --> 00:03:08,220
All right?

61
00:03:10,420 --> 00:03:11,260
Okay.

62
00:03:12,520 --> 00:03:14,019
Just wait. I'll make sure
you get your revenge.

63
00:03:14,020 --> 00:03:14,540
Mm.

64
00:03:14,580 --> 00:03:15,500
I'm leaving first.

65
00:03:20,340 --> 00:03:22,220
(I won't become the young madam
even if I go back.)

66
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:24,900
(But if I stay here, I might still have
a chance with Deputy Commander Cheng.)

67
00:03:24,940 --> 00:03:26,740
(I'm not going back just to be a maid.)

68
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:29,130
(I want to be just like Zhuang Yunqiu.)

69
00:03:31,620 --> 00:03:33,380
Let me go.

70
00:03:35,340 --> 00:03:36,779
(That voice...)

71
00:03:36,780 --> 00:03:38,740
(It sounds like the Commander.)

72
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:44,220
(What's going on?)

73
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:50,060
Stay here and keep watch.
I'm going to relieve myself.

74
00:03:51,060 --> 00:03:52,060
I'm leaving now.

75
00:04:27,980 --> 00:04:28,740
Commander.

76
00:04:29,050 --> 00:04:30,320
What took you so long?

77
00:04:31,780 --> 00:04:32,660
Hurry up.

78
00:04:37,300 --> 00:04:38,740
Gu Nianchi?

79
00:04:40,740 --> 00:04:41,760
Who are you?

80
00:04:42,180 --> 00:04:43,339
What happened to you?

81
00:04:43,340 --> 00:04:45,220
Why are you bleeding so badly?

82
00:04:46,740 --> 00:04:47,700
You're...

83
00:04:48,870 --> 00:04:50,540
I'm Xue Wan.

84
00:04:50,700 --> 00:04:52,420
We just met a moment ago.

85
00:05:00,900 --> 00:05:02,020
Xue Wan...

86
00:05:03,220 --> 00:05:04,540
My injuries are too severe.

87
00:05:05,740 --> 00:05:06,940
I didn't recognize you.

88
00:05:08,180 --> 00:05:09,300
What happened to you?

89
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:11,740
How did you end up so badly hurt?

90
00:05:12,380 --> 00:05:13,180
Commander.

91
00:05:13,300 --> 00:05:14,259
There's no time to lose.

92
00:05:14,260 --> 00:05:15,740
I'll go bring the car over first.

93
00:05:21,020 --> 00:05:22,140
Are you all right?

94
00:05:22,220 --> 00:05:23,300
What's wrong?

95
00:05:27,540 --> 00:05:28,860
Lieutenant Li?

96
00:05:31,820 --> 00:05:32,660
What happened?

97
00:05:32,940 --> 00:05:34,060
It's nothing.

98
00:05:35,700 --> 00:05:37,180
They're all Zhuang Yunqiu's people.

99
00:05:38,420 --> 00:05:39,860
Zhuang Yunqiu?

100
00:05:40,820 --> 00:05:42,900
Weren't you two just fine a moment ago?

101
00:05:44,580 --> 00:05:46,140
She forced me to do it.

102
00:05:47,020 --> 00:05:48,020
When I refused,

103
00:05:49,140 --> 00:05:50,540
she treated me like this.

104
00:05:54,620 --> 00:05:55,930
Xue Wan.

105
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:58,060
Help me.

106
00:06:01,860 --> 00:06:02,580
All right.

107
00:06:09,740 --> 00:06:10,780
Gu Nianchi.

108
00:06:10,900 --> 00:06:11,820
Gu Nianchi.

109
00:06:12,580 --> 00:06:13,540
Gu Nianchi.

110
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:17,400
(Yancheng Freed from the Scourge of Opium)
This poison should've been destroyed long ago.

111
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:19,100
It's ruined countless lives.

112
00:06:21,300 --> 00:06:22,620
Commander.

113
00:06:26,060 --> 00:06:27,140
This is...

114
00:06:30,210 --> 00:06:31,940
These were seized
from the dock warehouse.

115
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:36,640
And we also found them
using the coordinates of the Red Spider Lily

116
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:37,399
you gave us.

117
00:06:37,400 --> 00:06:39,330
These are the ones mentioned
at the Fragrance Gala.

118
00:06:39,620 --> 00:06:41,360
So you were the one
who confiscated them.

119
00:06:42,980 --> 00:06:44,739
These drugs have destroyed the people.

120
00:06:44,740 --> 00:06:47,080
They've ruined bodies, torn families apart,
and left homes shattered.

121
00:06:47,940 --> 00:06:48,780
Shaoyuan.

122
00:06:49,340 --> 00:06:50,580
You did well.

123
00:06:52,380 --> 00:06:53,220
Today,

124
00:06:53,940 --> 00:06:56,220
I'm going to destroy
all this opium in public.

125
00:06:57,980 --> 00:06:59,180
Wonderful.

126
00:07:00,380 --> 00:07:01,400
Wonderful.

127
00:07:04,340 --> 00:07:05,460
Then let's

128
00:07:05,980 --> 00:07:07,499
destroy all these poisonous things

129
00:07:07,500 --> 00:07:08,740
together.

130
00:07:13,900 --> 00:07:14,979
Prepare to burn the opium.

131
00:07:14,980 --> 00:07:15,940
Yes, Commander.

132
00:07:17,710 --> 00:07:19,009
Well done, Commander!

133
00:07:19,010 --> 00:07:19,969
From this day forward,

134
00:07:19,970 --> 00:07:22,730
- no one is allowed to sell opium in Yancheng.
- Well done, Commander!

135
00:07:22,890 --> 00:07:27,680
All right!

136
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:30,939
Well done, Commander!

137
00:07:30,940 --> 00:07:32,519
- Why haven't I seen
- All right!

138
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:34,320
the man who's always by your side today?

139
00:07:34,670 --> 00:07:36,330
His name is Cheng Yi, right?

140
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:41,020
He's handling something else for me.

141
00:07:42,850 --> 00:07:44,120
Destroy every last bit of it.

142
00:07:46,180 --> 00:07:48,059
- Yancheng is only getting better and better.
- Well done!

143
00:07:48,060 --> 00:07:49,890
The people will live happier lives too.

144
00:07:51,590 --> 00:07:53,299
I'll protect Yancheng.

145
00:07:53,300 --> 00:07:54,520
Including you.

146
00:07:54,650 --> 00:07:55,909
Don't leave a single bit behind.

147
00:07:55,910 --> 00:07:58,099
- This poison ruins lives.
- Pour it in.

148
00:07:58,100 --> 00:07:59,059
Then...

149
00:07:59,060 --> 00:08:01,819
may I have the honor
of inviting Miss Zhuang

150
00:08:01,820 --> 00:08:03,270
to come somewhere with me?

151
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:06,309
All right.

152
00:08:06,310 --> 00:08:07,990
I accept your invitation.

153
00:08:08,580 --> 00:08:09,480
Thank you.

154
00:08:21,290 --> 00:08:22,550
Don't open your eyes.

155
00:08:23,590 --> 00:08:24,970
Okay.

156
00:08:26,940 --> 00:08:28,220
The walk is a bit long.

157
00:08:31,820 --> 00:08:32,649
Watch the steps.

158
00:08:32,650 --> 00:08:35,579
When can I open my eyes?
Why are you being so mysterious?

159
00:08:35,580 --> 00:08:36,950
We're almost there.

160
00:08:38,340 --> 00:08:38,909
Come on.

161
00:08:38,910 --> 00:08:40,340
Don't open your eyes yet.

162
00:08:40,580 --> 00:08:41,500
Don't move.

163
00:08:52,380 --> 00:08:53,360
All right.

164
00:08:53,710 --> 00:08:58,420
♪Love quietly hides within the wind♪

165
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:05,090
♪How can broken love ever go on?♪

166
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:11,720
♪How much hope must fade into despair?♪

167
00:09:12,220 --> 00:09:15,800
♪In the blink of an eye,
everything falls apart♪

168
00:09:16,140 --> 00:09:19,150
♪Bound by the fate we cannot escape♪

169
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:24,440
♪You and I caught in
this tangled love and hate♪

170
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:30,750
♪Fragile hearts can hardly bear goodbye♪

171
00:09:31,810 --> 00:09:37,410
♪How many times
must pain cut deep before we wake?♪

172
00:09:37,950 --> 00:09:41,330
♪I once gave myself
to you so completely♪

173
00:09:41,580 --> 00:09:44,529
♪Still holding on to that heart♪

174
00:09:44,530 --> 00:09:49,669
♪Only to suffer your fatal blow♪

175
00:09:49,670 --> 00:09:53,989
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

176
00:09:53,990 --> 00:09:56,569
♪Yet I approach you with such caution♪

177
00:09:56,570 --> 00:09:58,849
♪How could a stand in ever have♪

178
00:09:58,850 --> 00:10:02,399
♪The right to be loved by you?♪

179
00:10:02,400 --> 00:10:06,929
♪If love is nothing
more than endless schemes♪

180
00:10:06,930 --> 00:10:09,460
♪Used and abandoned in the end♪

181
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:11,549
♪Still I walk into♪

182
00:10:11,550 --> 00:10:15,149
♪The trap you set without regret♪

183
00:10:15,150 --> 00:10:19,199
♪How desperately
I long to hold you close♪

184
00:10:19,200 --> 00:10:21,779
♪Yet keep it buried deep inside♪

185
00:10:21,780 --> 00:10:23,939
♪A stand in can never cross♪

186
00:10:23,940 --> 00:10:27,379
♪The shortest distance between us♪

187
00:10:27,380 --> 00:10:32,350
♪If love can
make someone lose themselves♪

188
00:10:32,510 --> 00:10:37,180
♪Then let me stay by your side♪

189
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,529
♪A substitute♪

190
00:10:41,530 --> 00:10:46,530
♪Needs no reason♪

